	 (83,153,'2012-12-11 22:55:25','Souta',NULL,14,'http://www.fanfiction.net/~ainekoyokai','United States','<p>I tend to ask extremely stupid questions. Yes, they''re stupid because the answer is usually right in front of me 99.9% of the time! (Even if I insist, at first, that it isn''t!)</p>

