	 (16,2,6,'9eda2fb4-08f5-4079-81f1-94c99e82426a','2012-12-11 20:47:22',26,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'In several episodes of DB:Z and DB:GT, it is said that using SSJ3 form is *very* tiresome to the user and works off energy in a matter of moments, compared to being in SSJ1/2/enhanced/mystic/etc.  

