	 (83,2,33,'aa3b965f-7fde-44e9-baed-8f83fdfc5699','2012-12-11 21:22:12',52,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Spirit Energy is a part of one''s life energy, like an extension of one''s soul.  When Genkai transfers her spirit energy into Yusuke to teach him the technique, it is incredibly painful for him to receive such an overwhelming amount of energy/soul at once.  His body takes time to adjust to the new levels of energy.','CC BY-SA 3.0'),
	 (84,2,34,'257bbf8a-9960-4f8f-9b5b-d620f86176f1','2012-12-11 21:22:37',43,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'I''m kind of fan of time travel stories, so I got a little disappointed with Steins;Gate.

