	 (208,2,85,'202878e1-4ac0-4ff4-9411-96ddd608a108','2012-12-11 23:07:22',NULL,'user74',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If the various "superpower" ninja traits are considered "blood traits," how is it someone like Kakashi, who is in no way related to the Uchiha clan, can use the Sharingan Eye technique? 

