	 (212,2,86,'12cd44b5-fde3-4711-87a8-339170f23e8e','2012-12-11 23:11:09',NULL,'user74',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Most ninjas probably don''t live very long by nature of their work -- they die on missions, they die in wars, they die in raids, they die by being ambushed by other ninjas, they die in testing, etc. However, the handful of ninjas we have seen who''ve lived past the usual lifespan seem to be of very advanced age.

