	 (225,2,93,'4bfcbdb8-0fd0-4918-a95b-634f08f571ea','2012-12-11 23:18:46',NULL,'user74',NULL,NULL,NULL,'*Gunbuster* is one of my favorite series, and I remember learning of a sequel series called *Diebuster*, or *Gunbuster 2*. 

What is the relationship between the two shows? I am not referring to one being a sequel to the other; I mean, story-wise, how does Diebuster''s story relate to Gunbuster''s? Do any characters cross over both shows? Are there references in Diebuster to the events of Gunbuster?','CC BY-SA 3.0'),
	 (226,1,93,'4bfcbdb8-0fd0-4918-a95b-634f08f571ea','2012-12-11 23:18:46',NULL,'user74',NULL,NULL,NULL,'What is the relationship between Gunbuster and Diebuster?','CC BY-SA 3.0'),
