	 (249,2,104,'d10b4bfc-b54b-4b19-8f72-15d2cbf0671a','2012-12-11 23:39:07',27,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'From what I understood, Sai had fulfilled his role in the world. He had trained someone with passion to continue his work alone, without his guidance. The path to the "Divine Move" is now cleared, and he''s no longer needed.

